-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ В§target-cell вҲҲ ready-set вҶ’ вң“

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 22: evaluate (iteration 3 вҖ” child is soft, LLM)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў evaluate
  given pick-cellвҶ’В§target-cell вүЎ child
  given targetвҶ’В§program вүЎ В§p1-parallel-confluence
  yield tentative-outputs[], cell-type

  вҲҙ child has вҲҙ body: "Ask a question about В«configвҶ’topicВ» the way a
    curious 5-year-old would."
    Substitute configвҶ’topic вүЎ "the moon" and evaluate via LLM.

-- LLM evaluation:
-- Prompt: Ask a question about the moon the way a curious 5-year-old would.
--
-- Simulated output:
--   "Why does the moon follow me when I walk?"
-- Ends with "?", uses simple vocabulary (follow, walk, moon, why).

  yield tentative-outputs вүЎ [question вүЎ "Why does the moon follow me when I walk?"]
  yield cell-type вүЎ "soft"

-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ |tentative-outputs| = |В§target-cell.yields| вҶ’ вң“ (1 = 1)
--   вҠЁ cell-type вҲҲ {"hard", "soft"} вҶ’ вң“

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 23: spawn-claims (iteration 3 вҖ” child has 2 oracles)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠўвҠў spawn-claims accumulate
  given evaluateвҶ’tentative-outputs вүЎ [question вүЎ "Why does the moon follow me when I walk?"]
  given pick-cellвҶ’В§target-cell вүЎ child
  given targetвҶ’В§program вүЎ В§p1-parallel-confluence
  yield В§claim-cells[]

  вҲҙ child has two oracles:
    вҠЁ question ends with a question mark
    вҠЁ question uses simple vocabulary
    Spawn two claim cells.

  yield В§claim-cells вүЎ [claim-child-0, claim-child-1]

-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ |В§claim-cells| = |В§target-cell.oracles| вҶ’ вң“ (2 = 2)

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 24: check-claims (iteration 3 вҖ” child's 2 oracles)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў check-claims
  given spawn-claimsвҶ’В§claim-cells вүЎ [claim-child-0, claim-child-1]
  given spawn-claims-*вҶ’verdict вүЎ [true, true]
  yield all-pass, failed-oracles[]

  вҲҙ Evaluate each claim cell.

-- LLM evaluation:
-- claim-child-0: "question ends with a question mark"
--   "Why does the moon follow me when I walk?"
--   Last character is "?" вҶ’ вң“
--
-- claim-child-1: "question uses simple vocabulary"
--   Words: why, does, the, moon, follow, me, when, I, walk
--   All common words, grade-1 reading level вҶ’ вң“

  yield all-pass вүЎ true
  yield failed-oracles вүЎ []

-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ all-pass = true if and only if failed-oracles is empty вҶ’ вң“

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 25: decide-freeze (iteration 3 вҖ” FREEZE child)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў= decide-freeze
  given check-claimsвҶ’all-pass вүЎ true
  given evaluateвҶ’tentative-outputs вүЎ [question вүЎ "Why does the moon follow me when I walk?"]
  yield action, frozen-outputs[]

  вҠў= action вҶҗ "freeze"
  вҠў= frozen-outputs вҶҗ evaluateвҶ’tentative-outputs

  yield action вүЎ "freeze"
  yield frozen-outputs вүЎ [question вүЎ "Why does the moon follow me when I walk?"]

-- decide-rewrite: SKIPPED (guard false вҶ’ yields вҠҘ)

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- STATE AFTER ITERATION 3: child frozen
-- Frozen: { config, poet, scientist, child }  Unfrozen: { combine }
-- Hash transition: h3 вҶ’ h4
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

-- вҠўвҲҳ eval-one-loop: ready-set was [child] вҶ’ non-empty вҶ’ ITERATE

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 26: check-inputs (re-evaluation вҖ” only combine remains)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў check-inputs
  given read-graphвҶ’cells вүЎ [config, poet, scientist, child, combine]
  given read-graphвҶ’edges вүЎ [(configвҶ’topic, poet), (configвҶ’topic, scientist), (configвҶ’topic, child), (poetвҶ’poem, combine), (scientistвҶ’fact, combine), (childвҶ’question, combine)]
  given targetвҶ’В§program вүЎ В§p1-parallel-confluence
  yield ready-set[], blocked-set[]

  вҲҙ config, poet, scientist, child are all frozen.
    combine: needs poetвҶ’poem (вң“), scientistвҶ’fact (вң“), childвҶ’question (вң“) вҶ’ READY
    All three inputs now bound!

  yield ready-set вүЎ [combine]
  yield blocked-set вүЎ []

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- вҠўвҲҳ eval-one-loop вҖ” ITERATION 4
-- ready-set = [combine] (non-empty вҶ’ continue)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 27: pick-cell (iteration 4 вҖ” select combine)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў= pick-cell
  given check-inputsвҶ’ready-set вүЎ [combine]
  yield В§target-cell

  вҠў= В§target-cell вҶҗ check-inputsвҶ’ready-set[0]

  yield В§target-cell вүЎ combine

-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ В§target-cell вҲҲ ready-set вҶ’ вң“

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 28: evaluate (iteration 4 вҖ” combine is вҠў= hard, deterministic)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

-- combine is вҠў= (hard cell). Its body is a deterministic string concatenation:
--   вҠў= document вҶҗ "POEM:\n" + poetвҶ’poem + "\n\nFACT:\n" + scientistвҶ’fact
--                  + "\n\nQUESTION:\n" + childвҶ’question
-- No LLM needed. Classical substrate only.

вҠў evaluate
  given pick-cellвҶ’В§target-cell вүЎ combine
  given targetвҶ’В§program вүЎ В§p1-parallel-confluence
  yield tentative-outputs[], cell-type

  вҲҙ combine has a вҠў= body. Evaluate deterministically.
    Substitute frozen values into the expression.

-- Deterministic evaluation (classical substrate):
-- poetвҶ’poem вүЎ "Silver crescent glows\nAbove the whispering pines\nNight breathes, soft and still"
-- scientistвҶ’fact вүЎ "The Moon is drifting away from Earth at a rate of approximately 3.8 centimeters per year."
-- childвҶ’question вүЎ "Why does the moon follow me when I walk?"
--
-- вҠў= document вҶҗ "POEM:\n" + poem + "\n\nFACT:\n" + fact + "\n\nQUESTION:\n" + question
-- = "POEM:\nSilver crescent glows\nAbove the whispering pines\nNight breathes, soft and still\n\nFACT:\nThe Moon is drifting away from Earth at a rate of approximately 3.8 centimeters per year.\n\nQUESTION:\nWhy does the moon follow me when I walk?"

  yield tentative-outputs вүЎ [document вүЎ "POEM:\nSilver crescent glows\nAbove the whispering pines\nNight breathes, soft and still\n\nFACT:\nThe Moon is drifting away from Earth at a rate of approximately 3.8 centimeters per year.\n\nQUESTION:\nWhy does the moon follow me when I walk?"]
  yield cell-type вүЎ "hard"

-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ |tentative-outputs| = |В§target-cell.yields| вҶ’ вң“ (1 = 1)
--   вҠЁ cell-type вҲҲ {"hard", "soft"} вҶ’ вң“ ("hard")

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 29: spawn-claims (iteration 4 вҖ” combine has 1 oracle)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠўвҠў spawn-claims accumulate
  given evaluateвҶ’tentative-outputs вүЎ [document вүЎ "POEM:\nSilver crescent glows\n..."]
  given pick-cellвҶ’В§target-cell вүЎ combine
  given targetвҶ’В§program вүЎ В§p1-parallel-confluence
  yield В§claim-cells[]

  вҲҙ combine has one oracle:
    вҠЁ document contains all three inputs
    Spawn one claim cell.

  yield В§claim-cells вүЎ [claim-combine-0]

-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ |В§claim-cells| = |В§target-cell.oracles| вҶ’ вң“ (1 = 1)

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 30: check-claims (iteration 4 вҖ” combine's oracle)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў check-claims
  given spawn-claimsвҶ’В§claim-cells вүЎ [claim-combine-0]
  given spawn-claims-*вҶ’verdict вүЎ [true]
  yield all-pass, failed-oracles[]

  вҲҙ Evaluate claim cell.

-- LLM evaluation:
-- claim-combine-0: "document contains all three inputs"
--   contains(document, "Silver crescent glows") вҶ’ вң“ (poetвҶ’poem present)
--   contains(document, "Moon is drifting away") вҶ’ вң“ (scientistвҶ’fact present)
--   contains(document, "moon follow me when I walk?") вҶ’ вң“ (childвҶ’question present)
-- All three inputs found in document вҶ’ вң“

  yield all-pass вүЎ true
  yield failed-oracles вүЎ []

-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ all-pass = true if and only if failed-oracles is empty вҶ’ вң“

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 31: decide-freeze (iteration 4 вҖ” FREEZE combine)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў= decide-freeze
  given check-claimsвҶ’all-pass вүЎ true
  given evaluateвҶ’tentative-outputs вүЎ [document вүЎ "POEM:\nSilver crescent glows\nAbove the whispering pines\nNight breathes, soft and still\n\nFACT:\nThe Moon is drifting away from Earth at a rate of approximately 3.8 centimeters per year.\n\nQUESTION:\nWhy does the moon follow me when I walk?"]
  yield action, frozen-outputs[]

  вҠў= action вҶҗ "freeze"
  вҠў= frozen-outputs вҶҗ evaluateвҶ’tentative-outputs

  yield action вүЎ "freeze"
  yield frozen-outputs вүЎ [document вүЎ "POEM:\nSilver crescent glows\nAbove the whispering pines\nNight breathes, soft and still\n\nFACT:\nThe Moon is drifting away from Earth at a rate of approximately 3.8 centimeters per year.\n\nQUESTION:\nWhy does the moon follow me when I walk?"]

-- decide-rewrite: SKIPPED (guard false вҶ’ yields вҠҘ)

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- STATE AFTER ITERATION 4: combine frozen вҖ” ALL TARGET CELLS DONE
-- Frozen: { config, poet, scientist, child, combine }
-- Unfrozen: { }
-- Hash transition: h4 вҶ’ h5
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

-- вҠўвҲҳ eval-one-loop: ready-set was [combine] вҶ’ non-empty вҶ’ ITERATE
-- Re-evaluate check-inputs to discover quiescence.

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 32: check-inputs (final вҖ” all cells frozen)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў check-inputs
  given read-graphвҶ’cells вүЎ [config, poet, scientist, child, combine]
  given read-graphвҶ’edges вүЎ [(configвҶ’topic, poet), (configвҶ’topic, scientist), (configвҶ’topic, child), (poetвҶ’poem, combine), (scientistвҶ’fact, combine), (childвҶ’question, combine)]
  given targetвҶ’В§program вүЎ В§p1-parallel-confluence
  yield ready-set[], blocked-set[]

  вҲҙ All five cells are frozen. No cells remain unfrozen. Quiesce.

  yield ready-set вүЎ []
  yield blocked-set вүЎ []

-- вҠўвҲҳ eval-one-loop: check until condition
-- check-inputsвҶ’ready-set = [] вҶ’ condition MET вҶ’ EXIT LOOP
-- Loop completed in 5 iterations (0 through 4), 33 frames total.

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 33: state-tracker (post-loop summary)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў= state-tracker
  given read-graphвҶ’cells вүЎ [config, poet, scientist, child, combine]
  given decide-freezeвҶ’frozen-outputs вүЎ [document вүЎ "POEM:\nSilver crescent glows\n..."]
  yield frozen-count, quiescent

  вҠў= frozen-count вҶҗ len(filter(read-graphвҶ’cells, c -> c has frozen outputs))
  вҠў= quiescent вҶҗ frozen-count = len(read-graphвҶ’cells)

-- evaluation:
-- All 5 cells have frozen outputs. frozen-count = 5. len(cells) = 5.
-- 5 = 5 вҶ’ quiescent = true.

  yield frozen-count вүЎ 5
  yield quiescent вүЎ true

-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ frozen-count is a non-negative integer вҶ’ вң“ (5)
--   вҠЁ quiescent = true when all cells are frozen вҶ’ вң“

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- QUIESCENCE
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

-- All exerciser cells frozen or skipped. No cell in the ready set.
-- Program complete.
--
-- Frozen cells (across all iterations):
--   target, read-graph, check-inputs (Г—6), pick-cell (Г—5),
--   evaluate (Г—5), spawn-claims (Г—5), check-claims (Г—5),
--   decide-freeze (Г—5), state-tracker
-- Skipped cells:
--   decide-rewrite (guard false on all 5 iterations вҶ’ yields вҠҘ each time)
--
-- Inner target program evaluation:
--   5 eval-one steps: config вҶ’ poet вҶ’ scientist вҶ’ child вҶ’ combine
--   8 total oracle checks: config(1), poet(2), scientist(2), child(2), combine(1)
--   All 8 passed вҖ” no retries triggered.
--   0 uses of decide-rewrite (no oracle failures).
--   File-scope вҠЁ? was available but never needed.

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- OBSERVATIONS
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў= obs-metacircular
  given В§26-cell-zero-exerciser
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "METACIRCULAR EVALUATION WORKS: cell-zero's eval-one loop executed p1-parallel-confluence in 5 eval-one steps across 33 frames. Each step is one complete cycle: check-inputs вҶ’ pick-cell вҶ’ evaluate вҶ’ spawn-claims вҶ’ check-claims вҶ’ decide. The exerciser is itself a Cell program вҖ” the trace IS a Cell document. cell-zero evaluating Cell is Scheme's metacircular evaluator for the LLM age."

вҠў= obs-confluence-demonstrated
  given В§26-cell-zero-exerciser
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "CONFLUENCE EXERCISED AT THE CRITICAL POINT: After config froze (iteration 0), three cells entered the ready set simultaneously: {poet, scientist, child}. cell-zero's pick-cell chose poet first (index 0), but any of the 6 possible orderings produces the same combineвҶ’document. This is the eval_diamond theorem from Confluence.lean, demonstrated concretely: independent eval-one steps commute."

вҠў= obs-fusion-both-substrates
  given В§26-cell-zero-exerciser
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "FUSION PROPERTY VISIBLE IN DISPATCH: The evaluate phase dispatched on cell type 5 times: config=hard (pass-through), poet=soft (LLM haiku), scientist=soft (LLM fact), child=soft (LLM question), combine=hard (вҠў= concatenation). Both substrates were exercised within one program execution. This is what makes Cell a fusion language вҖ” neither classical nor semantic alone suffices."

вҠў= obs-guard-clauses-clean-branching
  given В§26-cell-zero-exerciser
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "v0.2 GUARD CLAUSES ELIMINATE PROCEDURAL BRANCHING: The decide phase splits into decide-freeze (where all-pass = true) and decide-rewrite (where all-pass = false). On each iteration exactly one fires; the other's yields become вҠҘ. In R16, a single decide cell used procedural logic in its вҲҙ body. The v0.2 version makes the branching structural вҖ” visible in the graph topology, not hidden inside a cell. Zero wasted evaluations."

вҠў= obs-wildcard-deps-collect-claims
  given В§26-cell-zero-exerciser
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "WILDCARD DEPS COLLECT ORACLE VERDICTS: check-claims uses spawn-claims-*вҶ’verdict to gather verdicts from dynamically spawned claim cells. As spawn-claims (вҠўвҠў accumulate) creates different claim cells each iteration (claim-config-0, claim-poet-0/1, claim-scientist-0/1, claim-child-0/1, claim-combine-0), the wildcard re-resolves at each ready-set computation. This is the wildcard-meets-spawner pattern from v0.2 spec section 'Interaction with вҠўвҠў spawners'."

вҠў= obs-aspirational-oracles-in-loop
  given В§26-cell-zero-exerciser
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "вҠўвҲҳ ASPIRATIONAL ORACLES WORK AS DESIGNED: check-inputs has oracles asserting ready-set = [config] and blocked-set = [poet, scientist, child, combine]. These are correct for iteration 0 but stale by iteration 1 (ready-set becomes [poet, scientist, child]). Under вҠўвҲҳ management, these oracles are ASPIRATIONAL вҖ” they provide feedback signals but don't block freezing. The until condition (ready-set = []) is the actual convergence gate. This is exactly the v0.2 semantics for oracles on вҠўвҲҳ-managed cells."

вҠў= obs-file-scope-recovery-safety-net
  given В§26-cell-zero-exerciser
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "FILE-SCOPE вҠЁ? PROVIDES DEFENSE IN DEPTH: The file-scope recovery policy (retry max 2, exhaustion вҶ’ error-value(вҠҘ)) applies to any cell without its own вҠЁ?. In this trace, all 8 oracle checks passed and no retries were needed. But if any soft evaluation had produced output failing its oracles (e.g., poet's haiku had wrong syllable count), the file-scope policy would trigger retry with oracle.failures context вҖ” then вҠҘ on exhaustion. The safety net exists even when it's never activated."

вҠў= obs-state-hash-progression
  given В§26-cell-zero-exerciser
  yield observations

  вҠў= observations вҶҗ "CONTENT-ADDRESSABLE STATE PROGRESSION: 6 hash transitions trace the inner program's evolution: h0(nothing) вҶ’ h1(config) вҶ’ h2(+poet) вҶ’ h3(+scientist) вҶ’ h4(+child) вҶ’ h5(+combine). Each transition corresponds to exactly one eval-one step freezing one cell. The frozen set grows monotonically. state-tracker confirms: frozen-count=5, quiescent=true. Hash the document at any point = hash the state at that point. The document IS the execution trace."
